Titolo: FIFA 07

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: FIFA 07 (also known as FIFA Football 07 and FIFA 07 Soccer) is a football simulation video game developed by EA Canada and published by Electronic Arts under the EA Sports label.
It was the last game in the FIFA series to be released for the GameCube, Xbox and Game Boy Advance, and the third (although first in the main series) to be released for the Xbox 360 after FIFA 06: Road to FIFA World Cup and 2006 FIFA World Cup. It was also released for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 2, PlayStation Portable, and Nintendo DS.
FIFA 07 sponsored Accrington Stanley for the 2007â€“08 season, with the FIFA 07 logo displayed on the back of the team's shirts.

